1298
00:47:42,499 --> 00:47:43,898
You have to remember the sixth son.

1299
00:47:43,899 --> 00:47:45,299
(Prince Geumseong)

1300
00:47:46,469 --> 00:47:47,598
He's Prince Geumseong,

1301
00:47:47,599 --> 00:47:48,769
