1316
00:48:16,499 --> 00:48:17,559
"What should I do, Father?"

1317
00:48:18,229 --> 00:48:19,598
- The military.
- The military.

1318
00:48:19,599 --> 00:48:21,169
The power he had...

1319
00:48:21,699 --> 00:48:23,298
(Munjong said, "Prince Suyang is the only man to take on this task,")

1320
00:48:23,299 --> 00:48:25,008
