- the scholars of Jiphyeonjeon, - Jiphyeonjeon.

1328
00:48:42,519 --> 00:48:43,519
(Jiphyeonjeon)

1329
00:48:43,819 --> 00:48:46,728
which brought together wise scholars.

1330
00:48:46,729 --> 00:48:48,558
